* REQUIREMENTS

The `text-keepalived` package requires following packages:
  - Parsec >= 3
  - filepath
  - FileManip
  - pretty
  - syb

All of these are available from Hackage (http://hackage.haskell.org/).

* INSTALLATION
You can configure, build, and install all inthe usual way with Cabal.

  runhaskell Setup.hs configure
  runhaskell Setup.hs build
  runhaskell Setup.hs install

